      "description": "ValidationResult comparing CFD-predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) against in-vitro measurements from the FDA generic centrifugal pump PIV dataset across 5 operating points. Validation was conducted using the Ansys CFX solver configuration ansys-cfx-15-build-2024q3-2 (modelVersion 2024-q3-build-2). Mean absolute error across all operating points is 18.3%. Uncertainty bounds were propagated via Monte Carlo sampling (n=500) over inlet flow rate and rotational speed. This result was accepted as supporting evidence for the hemolysis credibility claim.",
